🎨 1. Visuals & UI Polish (The "Trust" Factor)

Modern Dashboard Layout: Sidebar navigation instead of tabs; persistent bottom player bar.

Data Grid Library: Professional spreadsheet-style view with columns for Genre, BPM, and Duration.

Smart Metadata Parsing: Automatically extracts "Genre" and "BPM" from the messy prompt text so columns aren't empty.

UUID Cleanup: displaying "Untitled Track" or the prompt text instead of ugly file IDs (e.g., 4948a...).

Album Art Integration: Displays high-res art in the player bar and "Now Playing" screens.

Lyrics Panel: A slide-out sidebar to read lyrics while listening.
Tooltips: Hover over long text (like prompts) to read the full content.

🛠️ 2. The "Pro" Workflow (Power User Features)

Producer’s Dashboard: A "Stats" tab showing Total Songs, Playtime, Storage Used, and Top Genres.

Prompt Vault: A dedicated text bank to save, tag, and reuse your best prompt "recipes."

Drag-and-Drop Export: Drag a song directly from the app window into a folder, video editor, or DAW.

Batch Actions: Select 50 songs $\rightarrow$ Right Click $\rightarrow$ "Add to Playlist" or "Delete."

Mini-Player (Focus Mode): Shrink the app to a tiny "Always on Top" bar for background listening.

📱 3. The "Killer" Features (Marketing Hooks)
Mobile Bridge (Wi-Fi): A "Scan to Play" QR code that instantly streams your library to your phone’s browser (no app install required).

Suno On-Air (Social Radio): One-click "Go Live" button that creates a public link (via Ngrok) so friends can tune into your station.

Global Media Keys: Play/Pause/Skip works even when the app is minimized.
Discord Rich Presence: Shows "Listening to [Song] on SunoSync" on your Discord profile.

💰 4. Business & Launch Safety


Freemium Model: "Free Tier" limited to 50 downloads/day; "Pro Tier" is unlimited + Radio features.

Crash Shield: A custom "Whoops" popup that catches errors and sends them to Sentry.io so users don't just rage-quit.

Auto-Updater: Checks version.json on startup to notify users of new updates.


